# freeCodeCamp UIKit — code ownership.
#
# GitHub matches the most-specific rule per path; later rules override
# earlier ones for the same glob. Default ownership lives at the top
# so every path has a fallback reviewer.
#
# Update when team names change. See `docs/v1.1-backlog.md`
# (repo-going-public follow-ups) for the rationale.

# Default — every path needs at least one dev-team approver.
* @freeCodeCamp/dev-team

# CI / CD plumbing — operator review required for workflow + composite
# action changes.
/.github/workflows/        @freeCodeCamp/ops
/.github/actions/          @freeCodeCamp/ops
/.github/CODEOWNERS        @freeCodeCamp/ops

# Architectural decisions + operator runbooks — keep in dev-team review
# (already covered by the default rule, listed here for discoverability).
/docs/adr/                 @freeCodeCamp/dev-team
/docs/runbooks/            @freeCodeCamp/dev-team
